<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Data Unavailable | ATECO</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 40px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-top: 5px solid #dc3545;
        }

        .logo {
            width: 180px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .warning-icon {
            font-size: 64px;
            color: #dc3545;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #1a1a1a;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .reason-box {
            background-color: #fff4f4;
            border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .footer-note {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #14ab55;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #0e8a44;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <img src="/images/AtecoLogoTransparent.png" alt="ATECO Logo" class="logo">
        <div class="warning-icon">⚠️</div>
        <h1>Record Currently Unavailable</h1>
        <p>We apologize for the inconvenience. The digital record you are trying to access is currently unavailable due
            to a significant technical disruption.</p>

        <div class="reason-box">
            <strong>Incident Report:</strong><br>
            Recent regional conflicts in the Middle East have caused severe infrastructure damage to data centers in the
            Bahrain region. This has resulted in the loss of certain database segments affecting our record retrieval
            system.
        </div>

        <p>If you hold a physical copy of this certificate, please refer to it as the primary source of truth. Our
            technical team is working to restore operations.</p>

        <div class="footer-note">
            © 2026 Arabian Testing Evolution Company (ATECO)
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>